  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3560670047" />
    <a title="Isabella" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/44378707-isabella"><img alt="Isabella" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1551520965p2/44378707.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3560670047?book_show_action=true">Oct 05, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Isabella" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Isabella" href="/user/show/44378707-isabella">Isabella</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/11186752-the-book-of-lost-tales-part-one">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44378707-isabella?shelf=anthologies-novellas-etc">anthologies-novellas-etc</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44378707-isabella?shelf=jolkien-rolkien-rolkien-tolkien">jolkien-rolkien-rolkien-tolkien</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44378707-isabella?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44378707-isabella?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44378707-isabella?shelf=2020">2020</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44378707-isabella?shelf=adult">adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44378707-isabella?shelf=ebooks">ebooks</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3560670047" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15235409942900793252"><b>Rating: 3 stars</b><br/><br/><i>The Book of Lost Tales, Part 1</i> is a great book to read before going to sleep, not because it was mind numbingly boring that you can&apos;t keep your eyes open after reading a couple pages, but because Tolkien&apos;s writing style is so calming. That being said, one really needs to grasp the earlier stories, because the vast majority flow on directly (so much so that they could barely be called separate tales). Not sure when exactly, but I will be getting to Part 2 sometime in the future.</span>
  <span id="freeText15235409942900793252" style="display:none"><b>Rating: 3 stars</b><br /><br /><i>The Book of Lost Tales, Part 1</i> is a great book to read before going to sleep, not because it was mind numbingly boring that you can't keep your eyes open after reading a couple pages, but because Tolkien's writing style is so calming. That being said, one really needs to grasp the earlier stories, because the vast majority flow on directly (so much so that they could barely be called separate tales). Not sure when exactly, but I will be getting to Part 2 sometime in the future.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15235409942900793252" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
