        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1746635457" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18084236306389818010">Overall I liked this one, lots depth and inside backstory into the development of, and earlier discarded versions of, what would eventually become the Silmarillion, all researched and expertly presented by Christopher Tolkien, and as always great history into Middle Earth, but even more so into the writing process and the writer’s working evolution as they craft their unique story.</span>

          </span>
