<span id="freeTextContainer8441250441085428522">The fact that there are lost Tolkien writings that actually PREDATE these early Middle-earth legends is truly insane to me. He really spent his whole life developing this universe.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review3435242153">
