<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/77678.The_Lays_of_Beleriand"><img alt="The Lays of Beleriand (The History of Middle-Earth, #3)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1374681487l/77678._SY75_.jpg" />
