<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18964.The_War_of_the_Jewels"><img alt="The War of the Jewels (The History of Middle-Earth, #11)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388380271l/18964._SY75_.jpg" />
